  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I even said to Mila-- we knew, already, in this time, that the family don't exist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That they cannot-- and when they survive, we will find out each other for sure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No question about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I decided to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We decided to go, this was in-- in June-- May, June.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was about-- still not feeling well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we decided to go any ways possible Mostly peasants are supposed to allowed only walking or grab a train, or some borrow or some, you know, villager give us a ride.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We came to Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In Bratislava, we decide to get to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I decided to go first on my own to Hungary, to Budapest, to find out and I left Mila in-- in the thing because was danger to ride on the train, particular for women, because the Russian soldier was killing, raping, murdering, beating up people, you understand what I mean?",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were wild animals in this time, particularly in this period of time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came to Budapest, and I found my friend, a very close friend of mine, who lives here in Los Angeles, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, Pol, go back and bring Mila here because I don't you to stay in Bratislava because you never know what happened.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hungary is still much better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You could-- when I saw the food over there, you know, and the store full of fruits, beautiful, and things like this, I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went back, and I always carry a little short bayonet for small-- you never know in these days, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I took her with me and we didn't-- on the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was raping-- raping, killing, murdering, throwing people through the window by the Russian.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
